OL,4,Cslammed by pro-runway campaigners
OL,6,F"As an island, we are totally reliant
OL,7,Fon affordable and reliable
OL,8,Fconnectivity and it is now quite plain
OL,9,Fto see that Aurigny cannot provide
OL,10,Fthis essential service."
