OL,13,Fyears about the benefits of extending
OL,14,FGuernsey's runway which it says would
OL,15,Fcost #21 million that could be paid
OL,16,Ffor through a visitor's levy and lead
OL,17,Fto greater competition with lower
OL,18,Fpassenger fares.
